title: Jenkins and Jonez - Ja Morant, the Eighth Wonder of the World

description:
The guys discuss Ja Morant somehow doing even MORE unbelievable things, Allen Iverson’s love for the current generation of NBA players, Gary Payton’s weird story about Shaq, being fired over a meme, and more.
